***********************************************************
BrickPi Scratch Code and Examples

In this repository we've placed the start of a Scratch library for BrickPi and Raspberry Pi.

For step by step instructions on how to use Scratch with the BrickPi, please see:  http://www.dexterindustries.com/BrickPi/program-it/scratch/


BrickPi is a Raspberry Pi Board that connects LEGO MINDSTORMS motors and sensors to the Raspberry Pi.

More information on hardware, firmware, and software can be found here:  http://www.dexterindustries.com/BrickPi

***********************************************************